body:
Please read the comments carefully. It says 

> The exported graph has the following input and output nodes.
> Inputs:
> 'normalized_input_image_tensor': ...

So when you export the graph, you don't need to provide this.

See this [post](https://medium.com/tensorflow/training-and-serving-a-realtime-mobile-object-detector-in-30-minutes-with-cloud-tpus-b78971cf1193) for some more details.
